text: Wangdue Phodrang District is one of the 20 districts in Bhutan. The administrative centre is Wangdue Phodrang. There are 15 village blocks: *Athang Gewog *Bjena Gewog *Daga Gewog *Dangchu Gewog *Gangte Gewog *Gasetsho Gom Gewog *Gasetsho Om Gewog *Kazhi Gewog *Nahi Gewog *Nyisho Gewog *Phangyuel Gewog *Phobji Gewog *Ruepisa Gewog *Sephu Gewog *Thedtsho Gewog Category:Districts of Bhutan
title: Wangdue Phodrang District
